===Dictionary notes===
[[Category:Dictionary notes]]
*'''Collins Word Exchange''' has only the sense for the braid on an officer's cap. It allows both the singular and plural spellings.
*'''Merriam-Webster Online''' has no entry for any sense in neither singular nor plural spelling.
*'''MSN Encarta Dictionary''' covers both senses but only mentions the plural spelling.